properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 29 at 1:28AM EST until January 29 at 7:00PM EST by NWS Tallahassee FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southeast winds increasing to 20 kt with gusts up to 25
kt expected.

* WHERE...Gulf waters from the Walton-Okaloosa County line to
Apalachicola out 60 nautical miles.

* WHEN...From 6 AM this morning to 6 PM CST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 6 AM THIS MORNING TO 6 PM CST THIS EVENING
